<div class="message">
    <p>Thank you for considering {{ENV.COMPANY_NAME}} for your warehouse fulfillment needs. We've analyzed your requirements and prepared a detailed quote that covers all aspects of your logistics and fulfillment operations.</p>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
    <h3>üìã Quote Summary</h3>
    <div class="detail-grid">
